  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201309/a68a77a126d04619946abfea48e74f74.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t(Reuters) - BlackBerry Ltd warned on Friday that it expects to report a huge second-quarter operating loss next week and that it plans to cut more than a third of its workforce.据路透社报道，黑莓公司在本周五预警，下周发布的第二季度财报有巨大亏损，并预计裁员三分之一。</p>\n<p>\n\tThe company, which has struggled to claw back market share from the likes of Apple Inc's iPhone, Samsung Electronics Co Ltd's Galaxy phones, said it expects to report a net operating loss of about $950 million to $995 million in the quarter ended August 31, due to writedowns and other factors.黑莓公司一直以来都在试图从苹果和三星手机口中夺回市场份额，但截至8月31日，受资产减值和其他因素的影响，该公司的运营亏损将高达9.5-9.95亿美元。</p>\n<p>\n\tIt said it will cut about 4,500 employees.公司称，这次可能会裁掉4500名员工。</p>\n<p>\n\tBlackBerry said it expects to report revenue for the second quarter of about $1.6 billion, of which roughly 50 percent is expected to be revenue from its services unit.黑莓同时称第二季度的总收入大约在16亿美金，其中有一半的收入都来自其服务部门。</p>\n<p>\n\tThe company said it plans to refocus its efforts on the enterprise and high-end consumer markets, offering end-to-end solutions, including hardware, software and services.公司将重新聚焦高端用户市场，提供点对点解决方案，包括硬件、软件和服务。<br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p534533/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p534533\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p532734/\">聪明人的10大特征 你身上具备吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p534270/\">世界很奇妙 11个你也许不知道的事实</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2